Everyone needs a task manager – and this Apple Design Award winner is adaptable enough for anyone. Organising items is as simple as dragging them where you want them, and the Magic Plus button makes it easy to add to-dos from anywhere in the app.
editorialNotes.short: Organise tasks, assignments and to-do lists with Siri shortcuts.

editorialNotes.standard: Odds are you aren’t in the market for a new calculator app. But you should be. A 2018 Apple Design Award winner, the app is gorgeous on your iPhone, iPad and Apple Watch, and was built to provide a seamless experience.
